scopecontent.p:
This collection consists of the professional and personal papers of Agnes
                    Michels. Materials include: research notes; drafts and manuscripts of books and
                    other publications; correspondence and minutes from the American Philological
                    Association; minutes from Bryn Mawr's Admissions and Curriculum Committees;
                    teaching and lecture notes for courses in the history of religion and Latin;
                    correspondence with students, colleagues, and family; and offprints.
